      "text": [
        " عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «لَوْ أَنَّ اَلنَّاسَ تَسَحَّرُوا ثُمَّ لَمْ يُفْطِرُوا إِلاَّ عَلَى اَلْمَاءِ لَقَدَرُوا عَلَى أَنْ يَصُومُوا اَلدَّهْرَ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1963 - Imam (as) said: \"If people were to partake in suhoor and then break their fast only with water, they would be able to fast continuously throughout the year.\""
        ]
      }
    },
